Resources,

applications, maps, and visualizations created by City staff centered on the City of Austin's open data.

City Clerk's Office

Campaign Finance Data Search

Users can search campaign finance data submitted to the City Clerk between 2016 - present.

Austin Watershed Department

ATX Floods

Using open data, ATXfloods is an application which informs you about low water crossings across Central Texas during flooding events.

Transportation Department

Transportation Dashboard

View the real-time open data about signal operations accessible to
everyone.
